Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在圣所看到马吉了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw Makee on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－马吉死了－我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Makee's dead. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲手杀的她\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I shot her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对圣所事件的描述\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your account of events on Sanctuary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人怀疑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}has proven dubious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们这帮混蛋怎么想的 我曾经也是你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know how you assholes think. I was you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他事可以做 其他的方式活下去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There's other things to be, other ways to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许放弃\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't you quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道凯瑟琳·哈尔西在哪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know the location of Catherine Halsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说不是钱的问题 对不对\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not about the money for you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她对你做了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's about what she did to ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦绝不会丢下你们任何一个人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren never would've left any of you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被捕了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比·安买下了索伦的船员\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Ruby Ann bought Soren's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我爸回来 他就会保护我们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}When my dad comes back, he'll protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他回不来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He's not coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想给你介绍个人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I want to introduce you to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是朱莉娅 她将是你的随从\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is Julia. She'll be your attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科塔娜  她很安全\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Cortana, she's secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你的问题有什么进展吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Have you made any progress with the problem I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管采取什么行动\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}All of my simulations returned the same result,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所有模拟结果都是一样的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}regardless of any action taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没什么可做的了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So there's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时在扫描波段\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I was scanning the band,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就听到了干扰中有声音\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and I heard something in the interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了一段信息\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You heard a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况还会再次发生\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你去寻找\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I want you to post your evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟其他活动的证据\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}of the Covenant's other activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按下按钮 我就会来找你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Press the button, and I'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新来的这人 让我们护送一个技术团队\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This new guy, he's got us escorting a tech team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,执行什么修复任务\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}on some fix-it mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要派钴队去另个通讯中继站\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If you're sending Cobalt to another comms array,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好告诉他们可能会碰到星盟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you better tell them to expect the Covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会授权银队\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I cannot authorize Silver Team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,执行战斗任务\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}to perform combat operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们可以作战了吗－是的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- We're cleared for combat? - Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务具体内容是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What exactly is the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在致远星的星盟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant's on Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有七公里到达目的地\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Seven clicks to target.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队三号 R队 这里是银队三号结束\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Cobalt Three, Romeo, this is Silver Three, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队队员 这里是银队三号\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Any Cobalt element, this is Silver Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正前往你处 收到了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We are en route to your position, how copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试下中继站\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Try the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦谢格勒中继站 这里是银队三号\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Visegrád Relay, this is Silver Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检查无线信号 完毕\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Radio check, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空中支援吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We getting air support for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦谢格勒中继站 这里是银队三号\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Visegrád Relay, this is Silver Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－完毕－就我们自己\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Over. - We're on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队指挥部不相信致远星上有星盟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}FLEETCOM doesn't believe the Covenant's on Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只认为钴队不见了而已\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They just think Cobalt's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次是搜救任务\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is a search and rescue mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们要考虑到钴队可能\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}but we need to be prepared for the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么东西了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}that Cobalt ran into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Something Covenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥部认为这个星球对方过不来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Command thinks this planet's untouchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没看到我们所看到的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They haven't seen what we've seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不如我们了解情况\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and they don't know what we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说吧 我们会不可避免地遇上他们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll tell you this, we will have contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之前 就只有我们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Until then, it's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这样合适吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This seem right to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看能不能恢复电力\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}See if you can get the power up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到 士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Copy, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走的时候很匆忙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Left in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有钴队踪迹 也没有破坏的痕迹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No sign of Cobalt, no breach marks at the--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚什么动静\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 从没听过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know, I've never heard anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过 在圣所听见的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I have, on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在信他了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You believe him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你队员把武器放下 士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell your team to lower their weapons, Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么意思\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-士官长  -立刻\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief? - Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都描述不出来你们处境有多糟糕\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't even describe the amount of shit you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都描述不出来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't even describe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸会发生什么事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}what's about to happen to your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这帮人谁啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Who the hell are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有舰队指挥部的头号命令\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I carry priority orders from FLEETCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－什么命令－将你们带回\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- What orders? - To bring you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妨碍了我的任务 让开\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You are impeding my mission, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任务\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There is no mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你偷了一架兀鹰－什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- You stole a Condor. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－伪造飞行计划－她说什么呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Falsified a flight plan. - What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在都不允许穿战斗装备\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're not even authorized to be in those suits right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更别提拿枪指着我的脸了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}let alone pointing a gun at my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以退下 否则我们就动手了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So stand down, or we will engage you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那祝你们好运\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长 我们该怎么办\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is Cobalt Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－最后机会－约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Last chance. - John.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我钴队在哪 要不然我就进去了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me where Cobalt is, or I'm going through that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来给你下命令的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I gave you an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What's the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下 不许开火\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Ah, stand down, do not fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－士官长－他们来过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief. - They were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以证明\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样证明的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一千英尺高的地方\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We were a thousand feet up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风在呼啸 电缆嘎吱作响\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}wind whipping, cables groaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的温度不超过2度\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Couldn't have been more than two degrees up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一月 懂的吧  －嗯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- January, you know? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我撑不住了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I can't hold it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被绑在安全带上 往下看\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm strapped in the harness, and I look down,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉亚瑟 说"我得释放一下"\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I tell Arthur, I say, "I gotta go."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他该怎么办\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What's he gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你尿在亚瑟叔叔身上了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You peed on Uncle Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尿他身上了 他能怎么办\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I peed on him. What could he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 抬下巴\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay, lift your chin up, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What the hell's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这故事很好笑呀\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This shit is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我以前听过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, I've heard it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又有什么区别\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What difference does that make?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我重复讲的时候你就应该笑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're supposed to damn well laugh when I repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老糊涂的人是我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm the one that's senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道你在抱怨什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know what you're complaining about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没在抱怨\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想抱怨来着\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, I mean, you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会替你保密的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your secret's safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是跟那件\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Is this about that thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该告诉我的事有关吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}that you weren't supposed to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该记得的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You weren't supposed to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得什么又不是我能选的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't choose what I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能得走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I might have to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没法带你一起走\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I can't take you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我知道－我想带的可是没法带\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- I know. - I want to, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那座桥了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You see that bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我阻止不了 爸\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't stop it, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那座桥是谁建的不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You know who built that bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我说了算的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太迟了－我建的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- It's too late. - I built that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你亚瑟叔叔\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Me and your Uncle Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竣工那天\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The day it was finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你妈 你姐姐一起踏上了那座桥\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I walked across it with your mum, and your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那会儿还不到13岁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She couldn't have been more than three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牵着她的小手\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Held her little hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不让我抱\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She wouldn't let me pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想一路走完全程\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She wanted to walk the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她什么时候来啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So when's she coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她走了 爸\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She's gone, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉娅走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Julia's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈也是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Mum, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就剩你跟我了－我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- It's just you and me. - I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I damn well know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别以为我不知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't think that I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我只是 对不起 有时候我脑子会糊涂\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sorry, I just, sorry, I just get confused sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不代表我不知道什么是真实的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Doesn't mean that I don't know what's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天见  好吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}See you tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 保证   －我保证\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Promise me... - Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 答应我别让他们把我活捉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No, promise me you won't let them take me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擅离职守\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Absent without leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未经授权使用武器系统\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}unauthorized deployment of weapons systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,违反\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}violation of,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们管偷一架该死的兀鹰叫什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I mean, what do you even call stealing a goddamn Condor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这违反了15项《军队统一法典》的规定\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm looking at 15 infractions of the UCMJ,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一项涉及将上膛的武器\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}one of which involves pointing a loaded weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指着军官的脸\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}in the face of an officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我干的 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I did that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官 我有可靠消息\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sir, I had credible information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那是感觉 是妄想\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You had a feeling. You had a delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你越界了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You went outside the chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Didn't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即生效\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Effective immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银队暂停作战\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Silver Team is suspended from combat operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到另行通知\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}'til further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯上将 我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Admiral Keyes, I know--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道个屁 因为你就不该知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You know nothing because it's not your job to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作就是服从命令\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your job is to follow orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队到过韦谢格勒 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Cobalt was at Visegrád, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四天前 钴队被派往阿克蒂斯四号\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Four days ago, Cobalt was deployed to Aktis IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No, this isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看过钴队飞行计划\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw Cobalt's flight plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－士官长－我看到了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief. - I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们给篡改了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They changed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我清楚自己看到了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰-117被解除现役\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}John-117 is relieved from active duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在通过精神评估之前\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and will be confined to barracks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得离开营房\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}'til such a time as he clears a psychiatric evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,117将接受精神化学检查\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}117 will submit to neurochemical--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的命令 还是阿克森的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Is this you, or is this Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰 别说了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}John, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整理服装 解散\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Rack your suits, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有试过为我们辩护吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you even try to defend us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你不用面对军事法庭审判的唯一原因\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm the only reason you're not facing a court-martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你骗我们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You lied to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把完成任务需要知道的事都告诉你们了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I told you what you needed to know to complete the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－根本没有任务－钴队就在韦谢格勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- There was no mission. - Cobalt was at Visegrád.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－士官长 能谈谈吗－是海军情报局干的 这一切\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief, can I talk to you? - This is ONI, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－是阿克森干的－不是吧 士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- This is Ackerson. - Come on, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不然他干嘛来这－听不下去了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Why do you think he's here? - I can't listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要去哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦纳克\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Vannak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你失控了－什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- You are out of control. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你脑子不清楚 反复无常\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're not thinking straight, you're erratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候也开始质疑我的判断了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Since when do you question my judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从你开始看见死人开始\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Since you started seeing dead people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在圣所看见马吉这事我谁都没告诉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't tell anyone you said you saw Makee on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰 我想帮你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}John, I'm trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想以朋友身份跟你谈谈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm trying to talk to you, as your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用不着朋友 下士 我要的是斯巴达战士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't need a friend, Petty Officer, I need a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不试着当个称职的战士呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Why don't you try doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,125 你不能解散\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}125, you are not dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是谁啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-关  -嘘\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Kwan? - Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你有危险－我看得出来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- You're in danger. - I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不   是鲁比·安要动你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Not from Ruby Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说你们的船员\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm talking about your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比·安把他们买通了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Ruby Ann bought them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－他们摆脱了索伦－什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- They got rid of Soren. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－接下来就是你－什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- You're next. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦是不是－我不知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Is Soren-- - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你赶紧带上凯斯勒走\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You have to get Kessler and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－拜托 我干掉你了哎－才没有\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Come on, man, I got you. - Did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吗 这个距离\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you kidding me, at this range?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 拜托 兄弟－这是士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Come on, man. - It's Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, it's Master Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卸八块了嘛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}in eight different pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 你打偏了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Nope, nope, you missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩呀\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有好消息\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We have good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞船修好了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Ship's fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以出发了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前说要几天时间的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You said it would take a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是索伦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们加班干了整宿  －过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- We worked all night. - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－没玩儿完呢   －凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- We're not finished. - Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能去吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Can I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－好呀  －不行\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Yeah. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Everybody goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一家人嘛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're all family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们先过去 我一会儿去飞船跟你们汇合\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You go ahead, I'll meet you at the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以等\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必麻烦 我能行的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't trouble yourselves, I can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－卡丽娜  －不麻烦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Carina. - It's no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡丽娜\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Carina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去拿你东西\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关 你可以出来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan, you can come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们当初加入海军情报局的时候 就想干这事吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So, when you guys joined ONI, is this what you had in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不喜欢这样 士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We don't like this any more than you do, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们再靠近点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If you get any closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就得谈谈此刻的感觉了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}we're gonna have to talk about our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是例行的心理评估 士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's just a routine psych eval, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－抱歉－什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Sorry. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－嗨－嘿 里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Hi. - Hey, Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把我们的训练取消了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They canceled our training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我干坐在铺位上 然后就\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I was sitting in my bunk, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就决定过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So you decided to come by here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看我发现谁了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Look who I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 一起吃晚饭呀\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, join us for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约会之夜泡汤了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There goes date night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会 别听他的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No, no, no, no, don't listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对约会之夜的想法就是他听着\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}His idea of date night ends with him falling asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卫星信号入睡 而我则去洗碗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}listening to the sat-link, and me doing the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝儿 不是你洗碗 是机器洗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Babe, you don't do the dishes, the machine does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总得有人按按钮吧 过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Someone has to press the button, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你饿了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You know, I hope you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭我给你治疗一下吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can give you some treatment after we eat, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来不是治疗的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, I didn't really come here for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我刚开始走\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Um, I guess I just started walking,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果发现不知道去哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}but it turns out I don't really have anywhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真服了 你让我好难过 泣就旦土土\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, for God's sake, you're making me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须得喝一杯了 坐\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Now we have to drink, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好漂亮\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It looks beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯身体可好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Louis' health?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝的这是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are we drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜欢的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聊聊吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前几天 你说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The other day, you said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的生活方式 其他事可以做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}there were other ways to live, other things to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道任务未经授权\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We didn't know the mission wasn't authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 里兹 瓦纳克\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Me, Riz, Vannak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We were in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And for the record,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长只是在做他认为正确的事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief was just doing what he thought was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这正是我担心的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, that's what concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很感谢你过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Look, I appreciate you coming down here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为你的指挥官辩护\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}to advocate for your CO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果士官长越界\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If the Chief went outside the chain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就需要纪律约束 我明白\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}there needs to be discipline, I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的存在不是跟这儿干坐着\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But we're not built to sit around and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们不好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要进入战斗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We need to be in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会改变决定的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not gonna change my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是让你改\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not asking you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正处于战时 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We are at war, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们仍然是你最好的武器\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're still the best weapons you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是建议我在没有队长的情况下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you suggesting I deploy Silver Team
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给银队部署任务吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}without its leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我一个\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时的 直到约翰没问题\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Temporarily, 'til John's cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有问题呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And if he's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可是士官长啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He's the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20分钟前\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Twenty minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰打晕了负责监视他的士兵\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}John incapacitated the soldiers assigned to monitor him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后逃离此处\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and escaped this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉你他的计划了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Did he share his plans with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划 什么啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Plans, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－什么计划－他在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- What plans? - Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次我们谈话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Last time we spoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问过你是否担心约翰的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I asked you if you had concerns
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神稳定性 你说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}about John's mental stability, and you said---
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－那是之前－什么之前\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- That was before. - Before what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样多久了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How long has this been going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我不知道－是科塔娜被移除后\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- I don't know. - Since Cortana was removed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是约翰跟星盟特工接触过之后\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}or since John interacted with the Covenant agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看过档案\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I reviewed the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在暗示什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我都清楚他已经失常了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You and I both know he's not himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯 我想跟你说件事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Look, Kai, I, I want to share something with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是以你上司身份告诉你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and this isn't me speaking as your superior, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候人是不会好转的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes people don't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是需要时间\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He just needs time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候 坚持会造成更大的伤害\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes, we do more damage by holding on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留下来看着他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't stay and watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我该怎么做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候需要几周才能来这里 有时候要几个月\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes it takes weeks to get here, sometimes months.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人根本就能撑到抵达\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Some never get here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们离开了牧歌星时是四艘飞船\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We left Madrigal with four ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到的时候只剩一艘了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We arrived with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那个了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.35,0:23:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,签订通行证之前 他们会把你安置在那里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That's where they process you before you're indentured.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是免费的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没有免费的东西\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Nothing is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于你所经历的遭遇\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}For what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多数人更惨\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Most people have it worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我觉得自己活该\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and sometimes I think I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我的惩罚\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm being punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－别这么说－这是事实\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Don't talk like that. - It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不该在这里的 这不是我的生活\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not supposed to be here, this isn't my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.26,0:24:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没能履行对我的人民和星球的责任\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I failed my responsibility to my people and my planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能因此责怪自己\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't blame yourself for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是关哈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm Kwan Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家族世代\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}My family protected Madrigal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.87,0:24:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在保护牧歌星\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}for more generations than anyone can count.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等轮到我的时候\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And when it was my turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.11,0:24:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.45,0:24:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该走了 我们可以混进去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's time to go. We can blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得立即行动\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We have to move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.64,0:24:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱了 他们会注意到你的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Take it off, they'll notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.08,0:25:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－是要躲起来吗－不是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Are we hiding? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.42,0:25:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们要去哪儿－去找你爸爸回来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Where are we going? - To get your dad back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.15,0:25:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要害怕吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Are we scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.49,0:25:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 跟紧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No. Stay close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.04,0:25:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把头低下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Keep your head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.94,0:25:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.61,0:25:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧往前走\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Rising forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.15,0:25:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续走\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.01,0:26:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－现在要害怕吗－系好安全带\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Are we scared now? - Strap in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.23,0:26:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会没事的 凯斯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Everything's gonna be okay, Kes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.23,0:26:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在就去找你爸爸\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're gonna get your dad now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.80,0:26:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.94,0:26:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不  不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.35,0:26:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们不会成功的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No, we're not gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.41,0:26:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳住\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.86,0:26:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.13,0:26:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.86,0:27:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.88,0:27:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.54,0:27:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我行动 然后带凯斯勒离开这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Wait for my move, then get Kessler out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.45,0:27:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－走舱门－你呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Use the hatch. - What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.42,0:27:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能把你俩送上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's worth enough to get both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.88,0:27:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－那艘运输船就够了   －不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- on that transport. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.09,0:27:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答应我你会把他带上那艘船\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Promise me you'll get him on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.79,0:27:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答应我你会保护他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Promise me you'll protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.32,0:27:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉埃拉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Laera!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.13,0:27:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不行 他们会杀了你的－妈妈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- No, they'll kill you. - Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.66,0:27:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开 拉埃拉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Open up, Laera!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.27,0:27:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿见\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.14,0:27:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别逼我把这门烧了啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't make me torch this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.01,0:27:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她出来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.18,0:27:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很识相 要不然有可能大家都不好看\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Smart girl, this could have got messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.01,0:27:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－拉埃拉 抱歉 我从没－得了吧 不是针对你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Laera, I'm sorry, I never-- - Give it up, it's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.35,0:27:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.46,0:28:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在中继站80米外\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We found Cobalt Team 80 meters
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.83,0:28:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现了钴队踪迹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}from the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.43,0:28:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在树上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They were in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.27,0:28:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在该区域观察到等离子武器留下的痕迹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We observed plasma scarring in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.47,0:28:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是打了他们一个措手不及\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't think they saw it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  队长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.71,0:28:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么处理\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How would you like to handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.61,0:28:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些尸体 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The bodies, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.82,0:28:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有尸体\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There are no bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.68,0:28:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－列为失踪吧－收到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- I would list it as MIA. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.19,0:28:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.03,0:28:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 上将\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You all right, Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.67,0:28:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.14,0:28:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.04,0:28:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是场悲剧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.71,0:28:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你知道吗－你说什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Did you know... - Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.85,0:29:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我们的士兵送进敌营的时候\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you know that Master Chief's suspicions were valid
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.09,0:29:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道士官长的怀疑是正确的吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}when you sent our soldiers out into a hostile--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.26,0:29:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢你的言下之意\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I resent the implication.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.06,0:29:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你知道什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I want to know what you knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.03,0:29:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想知道你什么时候知道的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and I want to know when you knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.76,0:29:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－冷静一下－冷静\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Just calm down. - Calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.93,0:29:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟就在这个星球上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant is on this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.83,0:29:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是时间问题\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It was a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.77,0:29:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一天总要来的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This day was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.20,0:29:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个数学问题 上将\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's mathematics, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.77,0:29:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次分析 每次模拟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}In every analysis, every simulation--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.17,0:29:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这他妈不是什么该死的模拟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is not a goddamn simulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.38,0:29:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是不是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Right, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.01,0:29:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的工作是决定下一步该怎么走\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But it's my job to decide what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.18,0:29:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须向指挥部发出警报\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We have to alert command.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.92,0:29:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你保证 你上级已经知道了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I assure you, your superiors are already fully aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.59,0:29:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要启动冬季应急计划\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We need to initiate the Winter Contingency.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.26,0:29:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即开始疏散平民\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Begin immediate civilian evacuation!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.06,0:29:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 上将 这次我们赢不了的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's over, Admiral. We don't get to win this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.57,0:29:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你发出疏散警报\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If you send out an evacuation alert,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.61,0:29:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会陷入混乱 恐慌\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}we'll have chaos, panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.14,0:30:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟部队几天前袭击了钴队\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant element hit Cobalt Team days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.04,0:30:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能假设星盟舰队就在不远处\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We can only assume the Covenant fleet isn't far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.48,0:30:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划是有的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There is a plan in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.25,0:30:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要做出些艰难的抉择\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}but it's going to require some hard choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.82,0:30:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道你是站在我这边的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to know that you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.46,0:30:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们不战斗了－我没这么说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- We're not gonna fight. - I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.93,0:30:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会战斗 只是不会赢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're going to fight, we're just not going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.67,0:30:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－这里是致远星－我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- This is Reach. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.51,0:30:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数百万人的家园\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Home to millions of people--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.24,0:30:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会尽力挽救\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And we will save what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.74,0:30:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－这里是我的家－也是我的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- This is my home! - It is my home too!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.75,0:30:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这不会让我付出所有\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't think for a second this doesn't cost me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.85,0:30:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是现实 上将\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}but this is reality, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.26,0:30:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要么面对 要么死\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We can either face it or we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.26,0:30:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们说话这会儿 重要资产\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Essential assets are being transported
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.67,0:31:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经被运出星球了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}off the planet as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.27,0:31:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去收拾东西吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get your things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.64,0:31:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要告诉任何人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.64,0:31:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会逃跑的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I won't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.44,0:31:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们能赢的那天你再去打仗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You'll fight another day when we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.35,0:31:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯上将 我能指望你吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Admiral Keyes, can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.06,0:31:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你妈的吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Go fuck yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.57,0:31:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's my husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.47,0:31:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－他还活着吗－安塔雷斯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Is he alive? - Antares?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.54,0:31:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不算迟 安塔雷斯－已经迟了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- It's not too late, Antares. - Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.85,0:31:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续  关\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Go on, Kwan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.33,0:32:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.16,0:32:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.36,0:32:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.60,0:32:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一会儿能见到她吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Will I see her soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.04,0:32:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说实话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.44,0:32:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.12,0:32:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－城里最棒的 来点不－不了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Best in the city. You want? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.03,0:32:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－试试－不了 谢谢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Try it. - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.41,0:32:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都有这方面问题\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You've always had this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.81,0:32:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你掌控不了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You are not in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.28,0:32:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说不听指挥\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You mean not controllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.05,0:32:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有过协议\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We had an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.21,0:32:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要给我带来的是信息 而不是关注度\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You were to bring me information, not attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.82,0:32:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有消息\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I have information.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.59,0:33:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想先知道你打算用它做什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But I wanna know what you're gonna do with it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.96,0:33:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有共同目标 就是赢得战争\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We have a common goal to win the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.59,0:33:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别误把我当朋友对待了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't mistake me for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.13,0:33:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.74,0:33:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为星盟在这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I believe the Covenant is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.91,0:33:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－在拉面里－在致远星上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- In the ramen? - On Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.35,0:33:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.75,0:33:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队斯巴达战士失踪了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}A team of Spartans went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.45,0:33:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队指挥部假装不知道发生了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}FLEETCOM is pretending they don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.76,0:33:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是星盟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And do you think it's the Covenant that--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.12,0:33:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是星盟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know it's the Covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.80,0:33:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建议你考虑清楚自己说的话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I suggest you consider what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.03,0:33:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我一直在做的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That's all I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.70,0:33:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想这事 一直在说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I've been thinking it. I've been saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.60,0:33:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可没人往心里去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And nobody seems to be listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.70,0:33:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－海军情报局知道的－小声点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- ONI knows! - Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.51,0:33:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海军情报局知道的 他们把真相掩盖起来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}ONI knows. They're covering it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.98,0:33:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为什么要这么做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.51,0:34:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海军情报局要保护自己\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The ONI protects itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.05,0:34:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们树敌\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Make them your enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.48,0:34:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便你是士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and it won't matter that you're Master Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.45,0:34:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也都不再有用\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you will cease to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.72,0:34:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一旦不再有用 那么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And when you cease to be useful, that--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.16,0:34:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不是 你没明白－你为什么要战斗 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- No, you're not listening, - Why do you fight, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.53,0:34:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－什么－你战斗 为什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- What? - You fight, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.87,0:34:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要赢 要保卫我们的家园\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}To win, to defend our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.37,0:34:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保护人类\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}To preserve humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.24,0:34:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错 你战斗是因为我让你去战斗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No, you fight because I tell you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.31,0:34:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个战士 就当好一名战士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You are a soldier, be a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.05,0:34:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你要做的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is what you will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.22,0:34:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.42,0:34:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去舰队指挥部\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Go back to FLEETCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.39,0:34:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该拍谁马屁就拍谁马屁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kiss whatever ass you have to kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.23,0:34:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去禁闭室服刑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You go do your time in the brig.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.66,0:34:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微笑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.83,0:34:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不许提这事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You'll never speak of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.10,0:34:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能会再授予你枚奖章\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They will probably give you another medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.61,0:35:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道我们都理解对方意思了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to know we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.88,0:35:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候离开海军情报局的 上将\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}When exactly did you leave ONI, Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.45,0:35:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你从这里走出去 那我就帮不了你了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If you walk out of here, I won't be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.69,0:35:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你就没离开过－别反抗了 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- You never left. - Stand down, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.19,0:35:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么认为\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.75,0:35:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来不知道他们其实那么脆弱\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I never understood how fragile they really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.82,0:35:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Fragile?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.72,0:35:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因为你让他们变成那样的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, because you made them that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.09,0:35:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还是孩子的时候你就把他们带走训练他们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You took them when they were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.06,0:35:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,训练他们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You conditioned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.96,0:35:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他们长大 可以独立思考的时候\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And then when they were old enough to think for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.93,0:36:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就确保他们永远不会去独立思考\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you made sure they never would.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.33,0:36:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把这些植入物放进去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You put in those pellets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.90,0:36:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就再也感受不到欲望\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So they never had to feel desire
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.94,0:36:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野心或者偏好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}or ambition or preference.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.34,0:36:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样他们就不会选择除你之外的人了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So they would never choose anyone other than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.75,0:36:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 对吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And that's it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.45,0:36:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你来干嘛的     －来跟你道别\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Why are you here? - I just came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.62,0:36:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.59,0:36:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我 我应该是想让你知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I, I suppose I wanted you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.10,0:36:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的努力没有白费 凯瑟琳\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}that your efforts weren't in vain, Catherine,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.60,0:36:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管你看不到那一天\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you won't be here to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.37,0:36:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你创造出来的东西 虽然可能破碎不堪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But these things that you made, broken as they may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.77,0:36:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但会成为某种\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}they're going to become the foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.51,0:36:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非凡事物的基\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}for something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.61,0:36:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望这最终能给你一些安慰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I hope that gives you some comfort in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.15,0:36:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不想知道她是怎么死的吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't you want to know how she died?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.13,0:37:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.10,0:37:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉娅 你以为我不知道她是谁吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Julia. Did you think I didn't know who she was?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.84,0:37:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们所有人我都记得\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I remember all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.31,0:37:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是你姐姐\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Especially your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.51,0:37:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她 好奇心很重\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She was... she was so curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.98,0:37:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问过很多问题\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She used to ask so many questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.85,0:37:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你永远不知道谁能挺过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But you never know who's going to make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.32,0:37:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增强手术 谁挺不过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}the augmentation and who isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.49,0:37:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没挺过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.43,0:37:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.86,0:37:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她快死了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.37,0:37:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不清楚原因 理解不了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She didn't know why. She couldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.17,0:37:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她说了你刚跟我说的类似的话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I told her more or less what you just told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.38,0:37:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是即便她看不到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That even though she wouldn't see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.62,0:38:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会是接下来前进的一小部分\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}she would be this small part of the next step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.13,0:38:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她听懂没\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know if she understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.89,0:38:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很害怕\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.76,0:38:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道她非常爱你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But I do know that she loved you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.70,0:38:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望这能给你一些安慰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I hope that gives you some comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.75,0:38:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.07,0:38:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要走了么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I thought you were leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.80,0:38:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想留你一个人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't want you to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.41,0:38:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是怪物\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.46,0:39:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二位重新认识一下吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll let you two get reacquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.43,0:39:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样我很难帮你啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You are making it very difficult for me to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.47,0:39:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 老大 我们要退出跃迁空间了－听到了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Boss, we're exiting slip space. - I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.64,0:39:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不拦着他们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I let them have their way...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.67,0:39:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你早就死了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}...you'd already be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.11,0:39:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对你很好 安塔雷斯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We were good to you, Antares.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.44,0:39:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh. Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.34,0:39:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你让我勉强度日\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you for allowing me to barely exist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.55,0:39:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟这帮傻瓜平分一份微薄的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and to scrape out a meager living split four ways
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.48,0:39:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活费 而你和你丈夫却把牧歌星的钱\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}with these bozos while you and your husband spent
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.62,0:39:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 都花在－你在说什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- all that Madrigal money on-- - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.55,0:39:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't play stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.12,0:39:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不傻\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.52,0:39:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一般都可以跟我丈夫讲道理\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can usually reason with my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.13,0:39:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要让他知道这事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}but when he finds out about this--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.83,0:39:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很担心 我最后一次见到索伦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not really worried. Last I see Soren,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.16,0:39:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他正在一艘开往致远星的囚舰上呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}his was on a prison ship headed for Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.00,0:39:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以踏实点吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So settle in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.04,0:39:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得有阵子了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It could be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.04,0:40:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你个王八蛋     －错 我是机会主义者\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- You're a son of a bitch. - No, I'm an opportunist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.68,0:40:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Now, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.22,0:40:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁去看一下怎么回事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Would somebody please deal with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.76,0:40:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被吵的都没法想事情了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't hear myself think.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.40,0:40:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.17,0:40:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道鲁比·安答应过你什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know what Ruby Ann promised you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.44,0:40:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你被耍了 安塔雷斯 现在还不算晚\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}but you are getting played, Antares, and it's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.04,0:40:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托别说了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Stop, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.28,0:40:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦什么都会跟你说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren tells you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.88,0:40:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他把东西藏哪儿了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You know where he's stashed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.71,0:40:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－藏什么－宝藏\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Stashed what? - The treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.59,0:40:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得很好笑是吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You think this is funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.12,0:40:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Because I guarantee you...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.40,0:40:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是哦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}...it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.20,0:41:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的宝藏就是一个装满\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What you call a treasure was a box full
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.07,0:41:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不值多少钱的氘币的箱子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}of deuterium tokens that wasn't worth much to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.24,0:41:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.74,0:41:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比·安不想要钱\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Ruby Ann doesn't want the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.98,0:41:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想要碎石星\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She wants The Rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.58,0:41:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.38,0:41:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何必要逼我呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Why are you making me do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.55,0:41:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我想让凯斯勒当孤儿吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You think I want to leave Kessler an orphan?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.29,0:41:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢那孩子的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I love that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.99,0:41:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在嘲笑你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She's laughing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.10,0:41:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听到那个声音了吗－听到了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- You hear that sound? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.13,0:41:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你觉得是不是该做点什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, you think you should do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.17,0:41:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在盯着她呀\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.31,0:41:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看看那是什么声音\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Go see what's making that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.76,0:41:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－藏哪儿了－她在拖延时间\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Where's the stash? - She's stalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.12,0:42:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能闭嘴不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Would you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.09,0:42:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得有问过任何人意见\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't remember asking anyone's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.26,0:42:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是舰长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.66,0:42:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的飞船\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is my ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.43,0:42:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你最后一次机会 拉埃拉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and this is your last chance, Laera.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.34,0:42:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.88,0:42:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉不了你 因为根本就不存在\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't tell you because it doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.21,0:42:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算真存在 我也不会告诉你的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And if it did exist, I wouldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.85,0:42:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚浪费了最后一次机会\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You've just taken it outta my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.99,0:42:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住 我也不想出现接下来发生的事的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Just remember, I didn't want what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.26,0:43:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有一分钟时间重新考虑你的立场\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You have one minute to rethink your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.27,0:43:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没必要走到这步的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It doesn't have to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.50,0:43:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Think of Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.77,0:43:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦在致远星 谁来照顾他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}With Soren on Reach, who's gonna look after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.01,0:43:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我我想知道的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Just tell me what I wanna kn--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.69,0:44:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯勒呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's Kessler?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.39,0:44:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.70,0:44:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关 我在问你问题\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan, I asked you a question--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.25,0:44:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我把他送上运输船了   －我告诉过你跟他待在一起的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- I put him on the transport. - I told you to stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.45,0:44:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我办不到－为什么不行\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- I couldn't. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.59,0:44:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那样你就死定了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}'Cause then you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.83,0:44:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟佩雷斯下士谈谈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to speak with Corporal Perez.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.67,0:44:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－她不在－她在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- She's not here. - Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.77,0:45:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是个好姑娘\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.08,0:45:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  女士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.55,0:45:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为恶魔在跟着你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But I think the devil follows you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.83,0:45:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几点了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.66,0:45:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很晚了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Late. - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.44,0:45:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会在这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.54,0:45:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我们聊过什么吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you remember what we talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.44,0:45:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You asked me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.98,0:45:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们活捉我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}To don't let them take me alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.39,0:45:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.49,0:45:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Today's the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.40,0:46:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.80,0:46:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.06,0:46:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呕\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.24,0:46:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人来看你了 爸\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There's someone here to see you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.62,0:46:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉娅\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.59,0:47:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉娅\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.25,0:47:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩雷斯下士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Corporal Perez.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.16,0:48:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从没进过教堂吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Never been in a church before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.43,0:48:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Mnh-mnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.17,0:48:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们来这里寻求安慰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}People come here for comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.80,0:48:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻求保护\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}For protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.14,0:48:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻求答案\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}For answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.55,0:48:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们如愿了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do they find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.45,0:48:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候可以\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.62,0:48:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.79,0:48:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在圣所的时候\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}On Sanctuary,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.20,0:48:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟出现之前我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}before the Covenant came, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.53,0:48:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在雾里 看到些东西\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw something... in the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.98,0:49:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说那个女人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You mean the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.48,0:49:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是真实存在的对不对\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She's real, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.32,0:49:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.65,0:49:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不着\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.39,0:49:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑子里一直响着那个声音\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't get that sound outta my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.44,0:49:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在圣所的录音\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is a recording from Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.11,0:49:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是段干扰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not just interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.58,0:49:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是个声音\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Not just a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.58,0:49:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有别的东西\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There's something underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.46,0:49:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.43,0:49:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一段祷文\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}A prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.44,0:50:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给予你们祝福 致远星的人们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I bring you blessings, people of Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.91,0:50:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我来时无有慈悲\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I've come without mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.39,0:50:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无有怜悯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Without pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.09,0:50:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是你们灭亡的工具\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I am the instrument of your extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.33,0:50:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将此星球献为燔祭\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I bring this planet forth as a burnt offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.75,0:50:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于这祭坛上 我放上恶魔的头颅\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Upon this altar, I place the head of the Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.13,0:51:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿他的鲜血引领通往光晕环的道路\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}May his blood mark the way to the Sacred Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.27,0:51:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝圣我的人民伟大的旅程\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and consecrate the Great Journey of my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.34,0:51:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是瓦尔加塔奈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I am Var 'Gatanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.28,0:51:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是 死神\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I am... Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.16,0:51:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They're already here...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.20,0:51:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Aren't they?


